---
---

<section class="oss section" id="open-source">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head scroll-reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">Open source</span>
      <h2>Hosted, or self-hosted.</h2>
      <p class="lede">
        DrFed is free and open source under the <a
          href="https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.html"
          rel="license">AGPL-3.0</a>. Use the hosted service, or run it on your
        own infrastructure.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="cards">
      <div class="oss-card scroll-reveal">
        <h3>Hosted service</h3>
        <p>
          Nothing to install; paste a URL and start debugging. Useful for
          investigating a production issue without setting up infrastructure
          first.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="oss-card scroll-reveal">
        <h3>Self-hosted</h3>
        <p>
          A single Docker image with built-in tunnel support, an embedded
          Postgres database (<a href="https://pglite.dev/">PGlite</a>) by
          default, and pluggable storage backends, for private or persistent
          deployments.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="meta scroll-reveal">
      <a href="https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.html" rel="license"
        ><code>AGPL-3.0</code></a
      ><span aria-hidden="true">·</span> Built with
      <a href="https://fedify.dev">Fedify</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(18rem, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .oss-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: clamp(1.5rem, 1.2rem + 1vw, 2.1rem);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .oss-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .oss-card p {
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-size: 0.98rem;
  }

  .meta {
    margin-top: 1.75rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }

  .meta code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    padding: 0.25em 0.6em;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--surface-2);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    color: var(--accent-strong);
  }
</style>
